	   <tr><td colspan=2>You all are forgetting the level and flag requirements needed to do the quest for item. You have to be flagged for either HoH or BoT (3rd tier plane) and be at least level 55 before the quest giver will give you the quest items needed to make the glove (monk emblem).<br><br>Its odd IMHO because most monks that i know of, usually have the epic by the time they reach the 3rd tier planes. I cannot picture them bagging their epic for a glove with much inferior stats. Even if you get 15/20 naked hands with this glove, most monks (at that level/planar flagging) I know of weild weapons that have superior ratio and stats than 15/20.<br><br>Its not an &quot;epic bagger&quot; item BUT I guess monks that have no tolerance for camping (for the epic) might have some use for this item.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
